{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "谢谢您，\\n海因瓦尔德大人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "不用跟我道谢。\\n重要的是将来，\\n一定要振作起来好好生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "男子",
            "context": "是。我会牢记海因瓦尔德大人的好意，\\n今后好好努力。\\n真的非常感谢您。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德……\\n刚才那个人是谁？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "他是我统治的领地的子民。\\n5年前犯了罪，\\n被判处流放5年的刑罚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗，是刑满回来了啊。\\n他好像很感激你呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "他是一家人的经济支柱。\\n考虑到他被流放后家人会生活拮据，\\n我一直资助着他的家人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶？资助犯人的家人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "犯罪的只是他本人。\\n就算是家人也不该受到牵连。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好厉害……\\n很少有领主能考虑这么周全吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这是身为领主的义务。\\n揭露他罪行的是我，\\n下令流放他的也是我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "既然如此，我就有必要\\n对他的人生负责。不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这次能等到他回来，\\n以后就不一定了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我可能不再是领主，\\n也可能会死去。\\n没法一直对他人的人生负责。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "说到底，这只是自我满足罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n有件事我一直在思考，\\n但至今还没有解开其中的奥秘。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那就是，我为什么要解谜？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为、为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "所谓解谜，就是揭开某个人的秘密。\\n而我也深切体会到\\n那可能会带来诸多冲突与不幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "解谜基本上就是多管闲事。\\n我虽然明白这一点，\\n却无法停止解谜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "究竟是为什么……\\n只有这个谜题我感觉无法解开。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为什么要解谜吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "海因瓦尔德，\\n你很聪明，也见多识广，\\n所以能思考各种问题并找出答案。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是有些问题，\\n不必由你来给出答案。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "嗯……是啊。\\n没必要特意掺和到事件里去解谜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我也这么认为。但……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，我不是那个意思。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "咦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "让犯罪者赎罪很有必要，\\n如果有人因此而不幸，\\n也必须伸出援手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这些都是你在做。\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你并不需要\\n全都独自承担吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我……独自承担？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。当你裁决某个人的罪行时，\\n援助他的家人\\n并不是你一个人的义务。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那是王和国家的义务。\\n要是一国之王能承担\\n如今你所担负的重任就好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我就是想让\\n这个国家变成那样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "国、国家吗……\\n厉害啊……\\n看来我的想法过于狭隘了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你所做的没有错，不必停止。\\n你也乐此不疲，\\n那样不也挺好的嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我一定会建立一个国家，\\n在这个国家里你所做的事\\n不会被当成错误。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "呵呵呵……哈哈哈！\\n太棒了，尤蒂尔。\\n真是精彩的回答！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "看来你是比我\\n更出色的解谜高手呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110280_01_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}